SPIRAL #1 - Blood Coral

Its the deep connection of life, vitality, wellness and prosperity. And it touches the very root of our energy. This indicates a sense of belonging, increased self-esteem and integrity.

Human emotions are different at their core across minds. But everything focuses on a single point of axis. They may vary, but it's often looped and spiralled.
